title: Add a Bulldoge - Bonfire farm with a 4.2x multiplier?
body: Bonfire is a newish Safemoon-esque coin with a strong 100k+ community and has been mooning this last week. To add fuel to the fire, let's add some Bulldoge to the mix for extra burning potential!
